author: lighteval
description:
The 2014 Workshop on Statistical Machine Translation:
    https://aclanthology.org/W14-3302.pdf

    The scenario consists of 5 subsets, each of which is a parallel corpus between English and another language. The
    non-English languages include Czech, German, French, Hindi, and Russian.

    For each language pair, the validation and test set each includes around 3,000 examples, while the training set is
    usually much larger. We therefore randomly downsample the training set to speedup data processing.

    Task prompt structure:

        Translate {source_language} to {target_language}:
        {Hypothesis} = {Reference}

    Example from WMT14 Fr-En:

        Hypothesis: Assemblée générale
        Reference: General Assembly

author: lighteval
description:
Wikitext-103 dataset from this paper:
    https://arxiv.org/pdf/1609.07843.pdf

    Gopher's authors concatenate all the articles, set context length to n/2 (n = max_seq_len),
    and use the "closed vocabulary" variant of the dataset for evaluation.

    In contrast, we evaluate the model on each article independently, use single token contexts
    (except for the last sequence in each document), and use the raw dataset.

The data was collected using comma EONs that has sensors similar to those of any modern smartphone including a road-facing camera, phone GPS, thermometers and 9-axis IMU.
Additionally, the EON captures raw GNSS measurements and all CAN data sent by the car with a comma grey panda.

推荐的上传方式是作者名.zip这样的压缩包并且压缩包中需要包含图片和标签，像是这样
作者名
├图片1.png
├图片1.txt
......
├图片n.png
└图片n.txt

其中，标签推荐这样标注：
作者名,标签1,标签2,标签3...

标签可以是手动标注，也可以是WD1.4反推标注，也可以是通过爬取图站信息来标注

可以。
